subject: The Moon?
author: eastern_paranormal
full_text:
Lately I have been getting a lot of chatter on one of my boxes claiming they are on the moon, and they even call me by my birth name in one long one. Anycow, I remember a year or two ago reading something on here about those claiming to be on the moon. Can someone refresh my memory as to who those were/are?

Gabreael
